WEBVTT

00:00:00.835 --> 00:00:02.049
I have to tell you,

00:00:02.073 --> 00:00:04.604
it's more than a little
intimidating being up here,

00:00:04.628 --> 00:00:06.882
an old American guy
trying to tell Africans

00:00:06.906 --> 00:00:08.987
something new about your own continent.

00:00:09.855 --> 00:00:13.578
But sometimes, an outsider
can see things in a different way,

00:00:13.602 --> 00:00:14.752
like from the air.

00:00:15.855 --> 00:00:20.042
That's what I found by flying low and slow
all over the African continent

00:00:20.066 --> 00:00:22.657
as I photographed
the spectacle of its diversity.

00:00:23.571 --> 00:00:25.419
And I wasn't always an old guy.

00:00:25.738 --> 00:00:28.086
(Laughter)

00:00:28.110 --> 00:00:30.659
This is me in 1979,